"Threat\"]\n    t1[Point]:::t\n  end\n  classDef s fill:#052e16,stroke:#22c55e,color:#bbf7d0,stroke-width:2px;\n  classDef w fill:#450a0a,stroke:#f87171,color:#fecaca,stroke-width:2px;\n  classDef o fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#60a5fa,color:#dbeafe,stroke-width:2px;\n  classDef t fill:#422006,stroke:#fb923c,color:#ffedd5,stroke-width:2px;\n```\n\n\n[SOURCE TEXT]:\n",
